Package org.aksw.deer.parameter

Interface Parameter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParameterImpl

    public interface Parameter
    A Parameter for configuring classes.

    A Parameter is made up of a Property, a ParameterConversion and either required or optional.

    Implementations of Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object) must mirror the respective behaviour of the encapsulated Property, that is, a Parameter's identity is agnostic of its ParameterConversion and whether it is required or not.
